b'\nToward honesty and transparency in rum....\r\n'

b'\nHonest this will be brief.    I hope those of you who are still considering whether to spend a lousy $17 to easily perform your own sugar tests, will now understand the TREMENDOUS value of having a complete database of as many rums as possible.   \r\n'

b'\nThanks to Johnny Drejer, any idiot like me can easily and relatively accurately test any rum from the comfort of their own home, mansion, sailboat or tent.   Distillers will no longer be able to hide or hope their rums are not tested by ALKO.   As a group our collections surely contain most all the rums being sold today.  \r\n'

b"\nFor those who are reticent, just order the damn equipment, and I'll walk you through it.   You can even just read the numbers, send 'em to Moi, and I'll calculate the sugar for you.   Feel free to email or PM any questions or concerns.\r\n"
b"\nNo excuses!   You're now either part of the solution or part of the problem (pun intended, lol)...\r\n"
